First Department,

August, 1977

(August 25, 1977) In the Matter of Thomas Venturini, Respondent, v Alice Sachs et al., Constituting the Board of Elections of the City of New York, Respondents, Bernard A. Rittersporn, Jr., et al., Appellants, and Lancaster M. Greene et al., Respondents.

Judgment Supreme Court, New York County, entered on August 23, 1977 unanimously affirmed for the reasons stated by Rubin J., without costs and without disbursements. Concur—Kupferman, J. P., Silverman, Evans, Lane and Markewich, JJ.
